ets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n本身我企前面背住佢，因為佢巳經屌到我唔耐煩，咁我咪好大聲講分手囉咁，之後靜左一陣佢突然一腳踩我隻腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n <br />\nBtw 炸 你老母"},{"pid":"932078dddfa61aa5609bb0e41d1ca6c5b2c10626","tid":61860,"uid":63105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T15:59:18.000Z","msg":"點解你可以忍受到佢成一年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0320574f8e2b57b318e0200562d2c7aafbdfc2f5","tid":61860,"uid":15932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T16:04:25.000Z","msg":"可能佢都苦練天殘腳等呢一日對付你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你應該慶幸唔係著釘鞋"},{"pid":"71fddc98a0c70f014e2ce286debf7a163a1e7a9b","tid":61860,"uid":35841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T17:03:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解你可以忍受到佢成一年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我九月份已經想提出分手，不過想睇下佢會唔會改下D脾氣，結果今日就變成咁"},{"pid":"37cb09d4949894532a18517b74e53cea1b4e4a9d","tid":61860,"uid":35841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T17:05:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>可能佢都苦練天殘腳等呢一日對付你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你應該慶幸唔係著釘鞋</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢有學泰拳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e610cc618b634946d5064a24bd82f83be40d858b","tid":61860,"uid":26829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T17:05:50.000Z","msg":"死肥仔腳"},{"pid":"b7c5580a22bcbd23f934462b29df4f9d2cb77a29","tid":61860,"uid":38630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T17:14:38.000Z","msg":"平時著新鞋刮損都痛到...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你都係消一消毒先 唔好焗住個傷口"},{"pid":"48165d3c3cab3321f7882109c91ad56dd624989b","tid":61860,"uid":59160,"li